Code for making a Shortcut tool for your Apphttps://alfrednutile.info/posts/141/Sun, 29 Mar 2015 00:00:00 +0000https://alfrednutile.info/posts/141/<p>This allows the user to easily make shortcuts to urls they are on and give them names.</p>
