<p>Here is the behat.yml for that, keep in mind I run this from inside of Vagrant (Homestead) and Selenium is running on my Mac thanks to &ldquo;webdriver-manager&rdquo; and brew install chromedriver you can see more on that <a href="https://www.alfrednutile.info/posts/129">here</a></p>
